---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="mt-auto bg-surface-dark text-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-10">
      <!-- Brand -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 mb-4">
          <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-accent flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
              <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z" />
              <path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5" />
              <path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-lg font-bold">KI-Tools Vergleich</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-sm">
          Unabhängige Reviews und Vergleiche der besten AI-Tools.
          Wir helfen dir, das richtige Tool für deine Arbeit zu finden.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Links -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-400 mb-4">Navigation</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/blog" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">Blog</a></li>
          <li><a href="/tools" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">Tool-Verzeichnis</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">Über uns</a></li>
          <li><a href="/rss.xml" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">RSS Feed</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Legal -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-400 mb-4">Rechtliches</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/impressum" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">Impressum</a></li>
          <li><a href="/datenschutz" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">Datenschutz</a></li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-5 leading-relaxed">
          * Einige Links sind Affiliate-Links. Bei einem Kauf erhalten wir eine Provision — ohne Mehrkosten für dich.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-gray-800 mt-12 pt-8 text-center text-xs text-gray-500">
      &copy; {year} KI-Tools Vergleich. Alle Rechte vorbehalten.
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
